Rasheedat Ajibade, Super Falcon’s midfielder, has joined Spanish giants, Atletico Madrid. The player made this public via her Twitter handle on Saturday, assuring that she will not take the opportunity for granted. She penned a one year contract that will last till 2022. “It is a great privilege and joy for me to be joining Atletico Madrid Feminino. It is an opportunity I will never take for granted, and I am ready to give my all to push this great club to even greater heights,” she wrote. The Super Falcons midfielder further expressed gratitude to God, her family, friends, and supporters. She described the move as a huge step in her career, adding that she was “looking forward to this great challenge with @atletifemenino.” “Great way to start the new year,” Ajibade tweeted.